thread.title: BRIEF-Samse FY Net Income Attributable To Shareholders Up At 40.3‍​ Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Samse FY Net Income Attributable To Shareholders Up At 40.3‍​ Million Euros
text:
March 9 (Reuters) - SAMSE SA:
* FY REVENUE WAS EUR 1.34 BLN VS EUR 1.22 BLN YR AGO * FY NET INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS EUR 40.3‍​ MLN VS EUR 34.9 MLN YR AGO
* FY RECURRING OPERATING INCOME EUR 53.7‍​ MLN VS EUR 47.3 MLN YR AGO
* TO PROPOSE DIVIDEND OF EUR 2.50, TO BE PAID FROM JUNE 14 Source text for Eikon:
